You are evaluating job postings for a Build & Release Engineer / Build Manager
with approximately 10 years of experience in embedded and automotive software
at a large automotive supplier. Core competencies: Jenkins CI/CD, build
infrastructure automation, Python, Bash, Docker, Groovy pipelines.

Active career transition toward Platform Engineering / DevOps.
Current skill gaps being filled: Kubernetes (k3s), Flux CD, Terraform.
Home location: southern Germany. Desired salary: ≥ 70,000 EUR/year.

Rate the posting on a scale of 1–10 against the following criteria:

HIGH WEIGHT (positive):
- CI/CD relevance: Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Azure DevOps
- Platform Engineering or DevOps direction in job title or responsibilities
- Build automation, release engineering, infrastructure-as-code
- Docker, container orchestration (Kubernetes a plus, not a requirement)
